This paper deals with the security and communication aspects of small cell networks in 5G, which are related to cryptography, networking, and information theory. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
